Text: Är det nan som fattar vad detta är, eller snackar sydlänningen bara dynga?

I've never studied Spanish but it says something like this: "The 5 parts of the manga series Dominion Tank Police. Very good."

It's quite easy if you have some patience to work out short sentences this. Look at it again and tell me you can't work out at least 3 of the words. Anyway, as the title says what it is s well as the category it's in, there's no need for bad language and almost racist comments (ja, jag tittar på dig heffaklump).

And yes, I do realise I sound like a prissy b**** and that I'm prolly gonna get flamed. Go ahead, I'm a big girl.
